    dc:creator "Cyriac, Vivek Philip; Narayanan, Surya; Sampaio, Filipa L.; Umesh, Pavukandy; Gower, David J." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Rhinophis Hemprich, 1820 (Serpentes: Uropeltidae) from the Wayanad region of peninsular India" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826370>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826368>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826374>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826376> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826370>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Map of southwestern peninsular India showing location of type localities of Indian species of Rhinophis. The precise type locality of R. fergusonianus is not known, so an approximate position for “Cardamom Hills” is shown." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826368>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Holotype (BNHS 3534: total preserved length 461 mm) of Rhinophis melanoleucus sp. nov. in life. Photograph by SN." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826374>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Heads and tails of two (of six) paratypes of Rhinophis melanoleucus sp. nov. Two left columns are BNHS 3537, two right columns BNHS 3538. Shown in dorsal (upper row), ventral (middle row) and lateral (lower row) views. Lateral views are of right (head) and left (tail) sides. Scale bars 10 mm. Photographs by SN." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826374/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826376>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Habitat in the vicinity of Lakkidi, Wayanad district, Kerala, India, the type locality of Rhinophis melanoleucus sp. nov. Left photograph shows general habitat of upland moist forest and grassland, right photograph shows floor of forest where R. melanoleucus have been found. Photographs by SN." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826376/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

